WEBVTT

00:02.550 --> 00:06.263
My mom lets me play outside in the afternoon.

00:07.389 --> 00:10.073
My mom won't let me play outside.

00:10.335 --> 00:13.505
I am always made to study at home by my mom.

00:15.960 --> 00:17.648
What are you interested in?

00:18.761 --> 00:21.706
I am interested in playing computer games.

00:22.109 --> 00:25.449
But my mom and dad won't let me play games.

00:26.517 --> 00:27.745
That's too bad.

00:30.153 --> 00:32.755
Jake's room is filled with garbage!

00:33.508 --> 00:35.811
We have to make him clean his room.

00:37.067 --> 00:39.913
I'm tired of telling him to clean his room.

00:40.189 --> 00:41.971
He never cleans his room.

